name: Boy Oh Boy Baby Shower Invitation
description:
This listing is for a high resolution digital file {YOU PRINT IT} of the pictured baby shower invitation design in JPEG/PDF format. This is a 5x7" size.

***No actual product will be shipped. I will email you your personalized digital file and you can print it yourself.

4 simple steps to order:

1) Add your choice to your cart, check-out, and pay through paypal.
You can pay through paypal with credit, debit, or your paypal account.
{You do not need a paypal account to check-out, simply 'check out as a paypal guest' at the bottom and use your credit or debit card.}

2) Provide the necessary info for your design in an email to me at greysquaredesigns <at> gmail <dot> com. (High resolution photo, information, etc.)

3) I will send you a proof within 24-48 hours of receiving payment and necessary info.
I will continue to make changes until you are totally happy with how it looks.

4) With your jpeg/PDF file you can print your item at home or upload and print at a local photo lab or print center.

Thanks for checking out Grey Square Designs!
